Day 16 — Event Delegation

Interview Questions:

What is event delegation?
:- let me tell about event delegation in javascript way to avoid multiple child event to create enstade we create on perent event to manage rest child event.
for example we can in form.



Advantages of delegation?
:- to avoid to many event creation. create one central event.

What is stopPropagation?
:- stopPropagation stop event from bubbling up to the dom tree. when child element trigger as event

Cross Questions:

Why does delegation improve performance?
by reducing the creating number of events.


